sed to announce that Contextual Related Posts crossed a quarter of a million downloads last week. Contextual Related Posts is a powerful plugin for WordPress that allows you to display a list of related posts on your website and in your feed. The list is based on the content of the title and/or [&#8230;]<hr style=\"border-top:black solid 1px\" /><a href=\"http://ajaydsouza.com/archives/2013/05/19/contextual-related-posts-crosses-250000-downloads/\">Contextual Related Posts crosses 250,000 downloads</a> was first posted on May 19, 2013 at 11:59 pm.<br />© 2003-2013 \"<a href=\"http://ajaydsouza.com\">Ajay - On the Road called Life</a>\". All rights reserved.<br />\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18:\"Ajay D\\&#039;Souza\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2364:\"<div class=\"KonaBody\"><p>I am pleased to announce that Contextual Related Posts crossed a quarter of a million downloads last week.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://ajaydsouza.com/?attachment_id=3105\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-3105\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-3105\" alt=\"Contextual Related Posts 250k\" src=\"http://i0.wp.com/ajaydsouza.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/Contextual-Related-Posts-250k.png?resize=300%2C245\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://ajaydsouza.com/wordpress/plugins/contextual-related-posts/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Contextual Related Posts</a> is a powerful plugin for WordPress that allows you to display a list of related posts on your website and in your feed.</p>\n<p>The list is based on the content of the title and/or content of the posts which makes them more relevant and more likely to be of interest to your readers. This allows you to retain visitors, reduce bounce rates and refresh old entries.</p>\n<p>Contextual Related Posts is one of the most feature rich related posts plugins for WordPress with support for thumbnails, shortcodes, widgets, custom post types, caching and CSS styles.</p>\n<p>What started as a simple piece of code by Mark Ghosh for his Weblog Tools Collection, has today evolved into a related posts plugin loved by thousands of users.</p>\n<p>I have several plans for the plugin and over the next few months you will find several new features being added. If you&#8217;re looking for support regarding the plugin, as usual, make a post in the <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/support/plugin/contextual-related-posts\">support forum</a>.</p>\n<p>Lastly, if you&#8217;re a user of this plugin and believe that it has been a valuable addition to your site, do consider a <a href=\"https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr?cmd=_donations&amp;business=DM9U98AGH74A8&amp;lc=GB&amp;item_number=CRP&amp;currency_code=USD&amp;bn=PP%2dDonationsBF%3abtn_donateCC_LG%2egif%3aNonHosted\">small donation</a>. You can enter the amount you wish to donate.</p>\n</div><hr style=\"border-top:black solid 1px\" /><a href=\"http://ajaydsouza.com/archives/2013/05/19/contextual-related-posts-crosses-250000-downloads/\">Contextual Related Posts crosses 250,000 downloads</a> was first posted on May 19, 2013 at 11:59 pm.<br />© 2003-2013 \"<a href=\"http://ajaydsouza.com\">Ajay - On the Road called Life</a>\". All rights reserved.<br />\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:97:\"http://ajaydsouza.com/archives/2013/05/19/contextual-related-posts-crosses-250000-downloads/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"